      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling factory-fresh. It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
