    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2002 BMW M3, a purist-spec example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis remains structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Performance is sharpened by a factory-correct limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension geometry. The exterior retains its original depth and luster, while the interior showcases pristine Nappa leather with negligible bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and free of parasitic losses, this E46 delivers a linear power band and tactile steering feedback characteristic of a true driver\u2019s machine.",
