    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece that has been preserved with obsessive care. This vehicle is in absolute concours condition, having spent its entire life in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is finished in its original factory paint, which displays a mirror-like depth and is entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or blemishes. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the wheels are pristine with no curb rash or oxidation. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather retains its original matte finish and 'new car' aroma, with zero wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the ambient lighting, operate with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, binder-organized service history that documents every fluid change and inspection performed by master technicians. This isn't just a used car; it is a meticulously curated collector's item ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
